descriptor.name: Red Velvet - Electric Red Eye Shimmer (6 ml)
descriptor.short_desc:
Minimum Order Quantity= 1 box
1 box = 20 Units
Price per unit= 450
descriptor.long_desc:
Glides like water colour, dries like powder. This quick-dry liquid textured eye shimmer is easy to layer and withholds onto your lids with perfection. Simply apply it, blend it and forget it. 

All of the Eye Shimmer shades feature dynamic runway-inspired colours that can be used as eyeshadow, eyeliner, or layered for natural to glamorous looks.

A sheer wash of colour, this shimmery formula feels like hydrating eye care giving a cooling effect on application. Diffuse for a natural makeup look or build for a bold one. A quintet of clean and high-performance ingredients works endlessly for your skin.

Mfg Date: April 2023
Expiry Date: March 2026

descriptor.name: Insto Aloevera Gel With Tea Tree Oil (500 g)
descriptor.long_desc: Made with the wonderful blend of Tea tree oil and pure aloe vera, it makes skin smooth. It is useful in treating rashes, dermatitis and allergies. It can also be used as a treatment for pimples, inflamed, and acne prone skin. Regular massage with this gel will improve the overall complexion and texture of the skin. Aloevera is a natural moisturizer & Tea Tree Oil has anti-inflammatory and antimicrobial properties.Suitable for all skin types.

descriptor.name: Insto Vitamin E Almond Oil Cream (500 g)
descriptor.long_desc: The cream is enriched with Vit. E and Almond Oil which is a source of vitality for dry and normal skin, contains almond proteins that stimulate new cell regeneration and growth, conditioning the skin, visibly firm and soothes it by removing dead cells. Stimulates cell metabolism and helps in slowing down skin ageing processes, fortifies the skin and restores its strength and resilience.
